\b Fix Me
\b0 \
There are two options for fixing the template if you accidentally save content into the template. The first is [Save as...] the page under a different name so you don't lose your edits. Then, just erase the offending content from the template and save. The other is to just ignore the problem and remove the offending content each time you need to start a new page. In either case, I recommend that you don't pick random pages from the info folder (of those that you already created) becaue if you make the same mistake again, you might delete content from a file that you wanted to keep. Even if you have content saved in the template, always start from there making sure the content is already save to another file.\
